mment('t1_2rh6')">[+] (3 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2rh6" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2rh6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">08 October 2010 12:01:36AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2rh6'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2rh6'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2rh6')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2rh6" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>You shouldn't waste your effort in attempting 1 in situations when you will almost certainly fail,</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Not quite. You want to consider the expected value of the attempt, not the raw probability of success. A 0.1% chance of curing cancer or 'old age' is to be preferred over an 80% chance of winning the X-Factor (particularly given that the latter applies to yourself).</p>

<p>It would definitely be foolish to waste effort attempting something that will <em>certainly</em> fail.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2rh6"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2rh6" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2rh6')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2rh6" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2rh6')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2rh6" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2t0/rationality_quotes_october_2010/2rh6?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2rh6" href="#2r1u" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2rh6" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2rh6')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2rh6 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2rh6" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2rh6" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2rh6" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2rim" class="morechildren" ><div id="pre_t1_2rim" class="parent"></div><div id="entry_t1_2rim" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2rim" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'></div><div id="display_t1_2rim" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"></div><div id="body_t1_2rim" class="comment-content"><span class="morecomments"><a style="font-size: smaller; font-weight: bold" id="more_t1_2rim" href="javascript:void()" onclick="return morechildren(this, 't3_2t0', ['2rim'], 3)">load more comments<span class="gray">&nbsp;(3 replies)</span></a></span></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2rim"></div><div class="comment-links"></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2rim" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></